Package: freebasic
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 freebasic-runtime (= ${binary:Version})
Recommends:
 freebasic-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: BASIC compiler compatible with QuickBASIC (fbc)
 FreeBASIC is a free/open source BASIC compiler largely compatible with
 Microsoft QuickBASIC.
 .
 This package provides the fbc compiler executable and driver, allowing
 FreeBASIC programs to be compiled and linked on Debian-based systems.

